RELEASE 0.1.5

* migration to Rails 2.0 and RSpec 1.1

RELEASE 0.1.6

* fixed bug in processing of options passed to generated finders.

* added descendants method which returns all descendant classes of a specified class which have been instantiated 

* fixed error in find_by_model SQL generation for empty string or array :conditions and empty string :joins.

* added support for count

* added column_names_hierarchy

* added support for table_names not following pluralization convention

